+  nand: Macronix MX30LF1G18AC
+  nand: 128 MiB, SLC, erase size: 128 KiB, page size: 2048, OOB size: 64
+  mt7621-nand 1e003000.nand: ECC strength adjusted to 4 bits
+  read_bbt: found bbt at block 1023
